Basic Pango Interfaces

  pango.item.lisp              Run the rendering pipeline          Pango 1.56
  pango.font-description.lisp  PangoFontDescription                Pango 1.56
  pango.font-metrics.lisp      PangoFontMetrics                    Pango 1.56
  pango.font.lisp              Representing abstract fonts         Pango 1.56 .
  pango.glyph.lisp             Storing information about glyphs    Pango 1.56 &.
  pango.attributes.lisp        Attributes for annotating text      Pango 1.56 .
  pango.markup.lisp            Markup language                     Pango 1.56 &
  pango.layout.lisp            High-level layout driver objects    Pango 1.56
  pango.script.lisp            Scripts and Languages               Pango 1.56 &.
  pango.bidirectional.lisp     Handling bidirectional text         Pango 1.56 .
  pango.gravity.lisp           Text layout in vertical directions  Pango 1.56 .

